            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Tree House High School is amongst the top schools which gives the highest quality of education. It enables learning in a safe, secure and nurturing environment. Opening with its first school in the year 2003, Tree House now function the largest number of self-operated pre-schools in India under the brand name of “Tree House” which is now across 33 cities in India. The School affiliate with the Council for Indian School Certificate Examinations (ICSE), New Delhi. The School offers best infrastructure facilities to give a complete learning experience to its students and the facilities which is offered by the school are Spacious classrooms, Modern teaching aids, Audio visual room and transportation facilities. Co-Curricular Activities: - The School will offer a collection of co-curricular and extracurricular activities like Outdoor sports: Badminton, Basketball, Skating etc.Indoor games: - Chess, Table Tennis etc. Yoga, Karate, Aerobics",
